        <div class="tour-content">
            <h1>Why Dairify Matters</h1>
            <p class="problem-statement">
                Every year, more farmers are forced to discard valuable milk due to antibiotic contamination ‚Äî
                a result of necessary treatments given to cows. But when contaminated milk enters the food supply,
                it poses a serious threat to human health and contributes to antibiotic resistance.
            </p>
            <p>
                Dairify is a smart, portable device that detects antibiotic residues in milk,
                identifies the type, quantifies the level, and even applies the correct enzyme to neutralize it.
                This process saves products, protects consumers, and prevents resistant bacteria from growing.
            </p>

            <img src="graph.png" alt="Antibiotic Resistance 2050" class="tour-image">

            <p class="stat-quote">
                üìä <em>"By 2050, antibiotic resistance could become the leading cause of death worldwide."</em> ‚Äî WHO
            </p>

